## TagFrames.EncodingTime type

The 'Encoding time' frame contains a timestamp describing when the audio was encoded. Valid timestamps are yyyy, yyyy-MM, yyyy-MM-dd, yyyy-MM-ddTHH, yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm and yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ss.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type EncodingTime = string;
```
